[02:02.970]Facing the change 面对改变
[02:05.320]But it’s still tough to see 但依旧很难看清
[02:07.900]At first I fought it all 起初我抗拒一切
[02:10.900]I was so mean 我变得十分刻薄
[02:12.900]I’m still unsure 我依旧不确定
[02:15.100]How it’s supposed to be 事情本该是什么样子
[02:17.470]But digging everyday now by the skin of my teeth 但我如今拼尽全力，每日坚持探寻
[02:22.070]Until I learn 直到我明白
